Fortis powers ahead with a significant investment in transmission.
Fortis completes acquisition of the largest independent transmission utility in the United States for US$11.8 billion.
“Fortis has grown its business through strategic acquisitions, and the acquisition of ITC, a premier pure-play transmission utility, is a continuation of this growth strategy.” – Barry V. Perry, President & CEO
Learn more about Fortis and ITC



















