Share Plans





Fortis Inc. offers a Dividend Reinvestment Plan (“DRIP”) to Common Shareholders as a convenient method of increasing their investments in the Corporation. The DRIP offers a 2% discount on the purchase of common shares, issued from treasury, with the reinvested dividends. The discount does not apply to optional share purchases under the DRIP.
(Offered to Registered Shareholders.)




Plan Document






Application Forms

Enrollment Declaration


Agent
Certification


Optional Cash Purchase –Canada



Optional Cash Purchase –U.S./Int.







Fortis Inc. also offers a Consumer Share Purchase Plan (“CSPP”). Under the CSPP, common shares are acquired from the Corporation at 100% of the Average Market Price. CSPP participants may transfer to the DRIP following their initial purchase to avail of the 2% discount offered in the DRIP.
(Offered to Residents of Newfoundland & Labrador and Prince Edward Island.)




Plan Document






Application Forms















