and Chief Executive Officer of FortisAlberta from 2007 to 2014. Mr. Smith served as
President and Chief Executive Officer of Newfoundland Power from 2004 through
2007, and as Chief Financial Officer of Fortis from 1999 to 2003.


He earned a Bachelor of Commerce (Honours) from Memorial University of
